Detailed Description

template<class Archive, class Elem, class Tr>
class boost::archive::basic_binary_iprimitive< Archive, Elem, Tr >

read serialized objects from a input binary stream archives stored as native binary - this should be the fastest way to archive the state of a group of obects. It makes no attempt to convert to any canonical form.
